posting_body: ['California Style Complex within walking distance of Lake Michigan and public transportation currently has one bedroom apartments available.', 'All apartments include refrigerator, stove, air-conditioner, carpeting, and blinds.', 'Each apartment includes FREE HEAT and FREE COOKING GAS.', ' (Tenant pays for electric.)', '1 Bedroom $725 --  $350 Move-In Fee after Application is approved -- no security deposit.', '2 Bedroom $850  -- $500 Move-In Fee after Application is approved -- no security deposit.', '$40 non-refundable Fee for Credit and Background check.', 'WE WELCOME YOU TO COME SEE OUR APARTMENTS.', 'If you would like to set up an appointment call:', 'KALABICH MANAGEMENT (708)424-4216', 'Hours:     Monday through Friday 8:00 a.m. until 5:00 p.m', 'Saturdays from 8:00 a.m. until 12:00 noon', 'You can also check us out on Facebook, our website <URL>, search for Kalabich virtual apartment tours at <URL> or go to Twitter(@KalabichMgmt).']
